Package gov.noaa.pmel.sgt.swing

Components that use the package javax.swing.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
Draggable Draggable defines an interface to allow classes to be imaged separately in a Layer from other classes.
 

Class Summary
ColorSwatchIcon ColorSwatchIcon implements Icon to create a icon that displays a small square of color.
JClassTree JClassTree displays the sgt object tree in a JDialog using a JTree.
JGraphicLayout JGraphicLayout is a abstract class that provides the basis for pre-defined layouts using the CartesianGraph class.
JLineProfileLayout Deprecated. As of v2.0, replaced by JPlotLayout
JPlotLayout JPlotLayout creates a pre-defined graphics layout for SGTLine, SGTGrid, Collection, SGTVector, and PointCollection data.
PlotMarkIcon PlotMarkIcon extends PlotMark to create a icon than displays the sgt plot marks.
UserIcon UserIcon extends ImageIcon to create a icon than can be dragged on a sgt plot displaying a user defined text string along with the image.
ValueIcon ValueIcon extends ImageIcon to create a icon than can be dragged on a sgt plot displaying the local coordinates along with the image.
ValueIconFormat ValueIconFormat is used to create the value string for ValueIcon.
